    %h2.center Community Development
    .row
      .text-block
        %h3.oss-text.padding2 Contributing to open source projects:
        %ul
          %li.link
            I am a maintainer of
            %a.link{ href: "https://github.com/rrott/cosnole.alert", target: '_blank', rel: 'nofollow noopener noreferrer' }<
              rrott/cosnole.alert
            \- a simple JavaScript library for displaying alerts in the browser console.
          %li.link
            do contributions to OSS in terms of security, like:
            %a{ href: "https://bsg.tech/blog/cve-2022-25854-stored-xss-in-yaireo-tagify-npm-module/", target: '_blank' }<
              CVE-2022-25854
            \- stored XSS in the
            %a{ href: "https://github.com/yairEO/tagify/pull/989", target: '_blank' }<
              @yaireo/tagify
            npm module.

        %h3.oss-text.padding2 Volunteering:
        %ul
          %li.link
            Worked as a full-stack developer, creating and maintaining the website for the
            %a{ href: "https://2019.nonamecon.org/" }<
              %strong NoNameCon 2019.
          %li.link
            Did the same for the annual
            %a{ href: "https://owaspukraine.org/" }<
              %strong OWASP Ukraine 2019
            Cybersecurity Conference held by
            %a.print{ href: "https://www.owasp.org/index.php/Lviv", target: '_blank', rel: 'noopener noreferrer' }<
              %strong OWASP Lviv
            Chapter

        %h3.oss-text.padding2 Developing local community:
        %ul
          %li.link
            Held
            %a{ href: "/blog/security/ruby-for-pentesters.html" }<
              «Ruby for Pentesters»
            %a{ href: "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QtZy5wvAVAA" }<
              presentation
            on the
            %a.print{ href: "https://www.owasp.org/index.php/Kyiv", target: '_blank', rel: 'noopener noreferrer' }<
              %strong OWASP Kyiv
